quote.summary: Xinte Energy Co Ltd is a China-based company principally engaged in the research and development, production and sale of the high-purity polysilicon, and the development, construction and operation of wind power and photovoltaic (PV) power plants. The Company conducts its business through four segments. The Polysilicon segment is engaged in the production of polysilicon and related products. The Construction of Wind Power and PV Power Plants segment is engaged in the construction of PV and wind power plants. The Operation of Wind Power and PV Power Plants segment operates PV and wind power plants. The Other segment is engaged in the manufacturing and sales of inverter, flexible direct current transmission converter valve, static reactive power generator and other businesses. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in the domestic market.
